1.3.name: colinmollenhour/cache-backend-file
1.3.description: The stock Zend_Cache_Backend_File backend has extremely poor performance for cleaning by tags making it become unusable as the number of cached items increases. This backend makes many changes resulting in a huge performance boost, especially for tag cleaning.
